            through secure Epic FHIR integration.
        </p>

        <a href="/patient-search/launch" class="search-button">
            Co-pay Assistant
        </a>

        <div class="features">
            <h3>What you can do:</h3>
            <ul class="feature-list">
                <li>Search patients through Epic's secure interface</li>
                <li>View patient demographics and insurance details</li>
                <li>Access Explanation of Benefits (EOB) data</li>
                <li>Review claim status and payment information</li>
                <li>Calculate patient responsibility and copays</li>
                <li>Track funding eligibility and available balances</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

